  "keyFeatures": [
    "Cross-platform game engine (Windows, Linux, macOS, Android)",
    "Multiplayer support with server/client architecture",
    "JavaScript plugin system with extensive scripting API",
    "Improved graphics and modern platform support",
    "Enhanced game mechanics and increased limits",
    "Scenario and sandbox gameplay modes",
    "Hot-reload plugin development workflow",
    "Custom game actions for multiplayer-safe modifications"
